                <note rend="inline" type="source">890d.00/226: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Beirut</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Knabenshue</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-10-23T19:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 23, 1925—7 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your October 23, 11 a.m. Department has carefully considered suggestion in
                    concluding sentence of your telegram but does not feel that it could
                    appropriately intervene in present situation. We wish of course to do everything
                    possible to protect American citizens if their lives are in danger. Keep
                    Department fully informed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
